    <item>
      <title>Hugo cheat sheet</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/hugo-cheat-sheet/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/hugo-cheat-sheet/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;create-new-page&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Create new page&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#create-new-page&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m using the &#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book&#34;&gt;Hugo Book&lt;/a&gt; Theme, which means it will render the content of the content in the &lt;code&gt;content/docs&lt;/code&gt; folder as a book.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;So the creation of a new page go as such :&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo new content content/docs/my-new-page.md&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;serve-locally&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Serve locally&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#serve-locally&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Simply use &lt;code&gt;hugo serve --disableFastRender&lt;/code&gt;. The &lt;code&gt;disableFastRender&lt;/code&gt; option is there to ensure proper site construction, when you add page, for example.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;publish-website&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Publish website&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#publish-website&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m using &#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://rclone.org/&#34;&gt;rclone&lt;/a&gt;, which is set with a SFTP remote named &lt;code&gt;docs.kntc.be&lt;/code&gt;. Enter the following commands :&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Links</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/links/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/links/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;useful-links&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Useful links&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#useful-links&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is an amalgamation of the websites I use regularly :&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://dnschecker.org/&#34;&gt;DNS Checker&lt;/a&gt; : Useful to check if the new subdomain you&amp;rsquo;ve just created/modified is live.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/&#34;&gt;Qualys SSL Checker&lt;/a&gt; : Check the quality of your SSL deployment.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tips</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/hacks/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/hacks/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;tips&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Tips&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#tips&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This sections covers things I don&amp;rsquo;t do often, but I&amp;rsquo;m happy to know they exist.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;set-default-path-in-rclone&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Set default path in rclone&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#set-default-path-in-rclone&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Usually, I set up &#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://rclone.org/&#34;&gt;rclone&lt;/a&gt; to use SFTP. It works, but always ask for the path to destination folder, with no way to set a default path. A solution is to add an alias to your config file (default path &lt;code&gt;~/.config/rclone/rclone.conf&lt;/code&gt;), as shown hereunder.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;display:grid;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;[rclone_sftp]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;type = sftp&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;host = docs.kntc.be&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex; background-color:#dfdfdf&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;user = YOUR_SSH_USER&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex; background-color:#dfdfdf&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;pass = HASHED_SSH_PASSWORD&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;shell_type = unix&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;md5sum_command = md5sum&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sha1sum_command = sha1sum&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;[docs.kntc.be]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;type = alias&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex; background-color:#dfdfdf&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;remote = rclone_sftp:DEFAULT/PATH/&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t forget to edit the highlighted lines.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
